{"tid":1148884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"飛機既發明真係好神奇","createTime":"2019-05-10T18:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T18:22:46.000Z","uid":199559,"like":21,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ced56f59f28ff46529a69c3f5bd0b62c3294d441","tid":1148884,"uid":199559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:02:34.000Z","msg":"每一次搭飛機 都會覺得幾百人<br />\n向住同一個方向坐好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又會諗人可以喺天上飛好神奇<br />\n碌ig就係睇啲飛機起飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n望住飛機既pat pat<br />\n咁重都飛到好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗快啲到另一個地方<br />\n好似大大力踢粒波岀去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解會發展得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快到 自己已經當擁有既係必然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同樓豬會有一樣諗法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓豬是個on9仔"},{"pid":"9453cdeb87fdd6bfe953a1985542983389647e75","tid":1148884,"uid":199559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"一齊講下你地有冇覺得好神奇既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a013bf16705a5520b818347933232ff639cd6ce5","tid":1148884,"uid":127532,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得最神奇係科學發達成咁，仲有咁多迷信撚"},{"pid":"d46b6032bf2377d006dd3f92d3c82dc1ba81cea8","tid":1148884,"uid":199559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a013bf16705a5520b818347933232ff639cd6ce5","tid":1148884,"uid":127532,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得最神奇係科學發達成咁，仲有咁多迷信撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f394ad1684edeff7af61455c17d64377ecbca8","tid":1148884,"uid":247796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:10:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得最神奇嘅係 咁多依家呢個年代仲係有無奇不有呢個四隻字"},{"pid":"c3d147d62d7f2b724be1834519d1d6d9d3e607c2","tid":1148884,"uid":247796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82f394ad1684edeff7af61455c17d64377ecbca8","tid":1148884,"uid":247796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:10:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得最神奇嘅係 咁多依家呢個年代仲係有無奇不有呢個四隻字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:11:06.000Z","msg":"打多左（咁多）"},{"pid":"df2aaca8e85d8a86ec7c85cef3e312c200159057","tid":1148884,"uid":129704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"宗教嘅發明 真係好神奇 明明係假仍然有咁多人信"},{"pid":"2dc4baf2969790c093c9e123054cc0ff7391fa1c","tid":1148884,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:14:02.000Z","msg":"我覺得電腦最神奇。<br />\n<br />\n明明只係一塊板。<br />\n點入面可以有記憶。<br />\n<br />\n邊個發明物件可以記憶，同顯示。"},{"pid":"dc3f4f0af04702fcf4e002ac199d50fdc314fa29","tid":1148884,"uid":21831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dc4baf2969790c093c9e123054cc0ff7391fa1c","tid":1148884,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:14:02.000Z","msg":"我覺得電腦最神奇。<br />\n<br />\n明明只係一塊板。<br />\n點入面可以有記憶。<br />\n<br />\n邊個發明物件可以記憶，同顯示。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"真係，我都諗唔明點將data記憶係ram同hdd度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d5a1de2bd907c704e700c092a5a41c1b8ed5d8","tid":1148884,"uid":199559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:17:15.000Z","msg":"同埋覺得飛機上面食飛機餐好可憐<br />\n唔好屌我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為情況就好似搭巴士有人問你食咩<br />\n怪但講唔岀有咩怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似大人問小朋友你想食咩<br />\n有啲小朋友會因為某啲事<br />\n而喺座位上面發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭飛機好似喺巴士食杯麵無分別<br />\n每一樣都係普通既食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係每個人都好似好期待<br />\n<br />\n情況就好似番到以前小學咁<br />\n一到某個時間就放飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有飯長負責派飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47286bd6360d520fbb8d3fe674b4318b770f8797","tid":1148884,"uid":199559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"手機識播歌都好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟點解可以識得發聲"},{"pid":"8076e992369827220349c38a26cb1f6d4ae6fcab","tid":1148884,"uid":199559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得整論壇/網頁都好神奇<br />\n<br />\n點解可以設計到個版面<br />\n啲位又識得好「合現」咁呈現岀黎<br />\n<br />\n即係打code係一段文字<br />\n點解可以有功能 顏色"}]}